LSOF
    lsof /var/log/messages
    
    all files in directory:
      lsof +d <dir>
      
    All files in dir and subdir
       lsof +D <dir>
       
  Umount busy?  -- this trick only works if /home is a separate partition
     umount /home
     umount: /home: device is busy
     kill $(lsof -t /home)
     umount /home
